title: [Caelyna's Boutique, Parlor]
description: Green specks add color to the thick ivory carpet that cushions the floor.  Centered in the room is a small linden table that holds a variety of refreshments.  A large sofa padded with dark green cushions and a pair of chairs are placed in a circular pattern about the room.  Standing next to a dressing room door is a polished gold-framed mirror.
